# AsiyaUI Consistency Rule

For any UI-related change in this project:

- Follow the AsiyaUI guide in `docs/ASIYAUI.md`.
- Preserve the current product feel: clean light UI, bold readable contrast, and friendly rounded surfaces.
- Use Tailwind color tokens from `tailwind.config.ts` (`accent`, `off-white`, `light-bg`, `dark-bg`, `white`) instead of ad-hoc palette choices.
- Ensure visible accent usage across screens via actions, highlights, or separators (not only one isolated button).
- Keep spacing and card separation clear for scanability.

When visual design behavior changes, update `docs/ASIYAUI.md` in the same task to reflect the new standard.
